            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國啟動200億美元海事再保險計畫 以緩解中東石油貿易壓力",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 由於美以攻擊伊朗導致霍爾木茲海峽航運幾乎陷於停滯，川普政府宣布了一項規模200億美元的再保險計畫，旨在重振該地區航運。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國國際開發金融公司(DFC)周五表示，正在海灣地區部署包括戰爭險在內的海事再保險，以穩定商業貿易。根據一份聲明，該機制將以「滾動方式」為至多約200億美元的損失提供保險，且目前僅適用於船隻。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：能源危機山雨欲來 霍爾木茲海峽困住中東石油出口</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在此公告發布前幾天，隨著油價飆升，川普要求DFC以「非常合理的價格」提供保險擔保，以確保海灣地區能源供應和其他商業貿易流動。在他發表此番言論之前，包括美國在內的一些政府曾暗示保險獲取困難是阻礙通行的一個因素。川普還表示，美國軍方可能會在海峽為過往船隻護航，但他目前尚未宣布具體計畫。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-85a0eb39-95d8-364a-a824-4c4811ed3ee3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">全球約五分之一的海運石油，以及天然氣、化肥和其他產品都經過該海峽。伊朗已威脅要襲擊試圖通過該水道的船隻，這加劇了石油和其他燃料價格的飆升。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家開發機構在提到美軍中央司令部時表示，「DFC和財政部正與美國中央司令部密切協調實施該計畫的後續步驟」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">DFC表示，已確定了「一流的美國保險合作夥伴」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Launches $20 Billion Reinsurance Plan to Ease Gulf Oil Trade</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Alexandre Rajbhandari.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95200%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%B5%B7%E4%BA%8B%E5%86%8D%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-%E4%BB%A5%E7%B7%A9%E8%A7%A3%E4%B8%AD%E6%9D%B1%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B-224400690.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-07 07:22:39",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "印度獲開綠燈後 貝森特稱美國可能進一步放行俄羅斯原油",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國財政部長斯科特·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:貝森特;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/貝森特\">貝森特</a>表示，美國可能解除對<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:俄羅斯;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/俄羅斯\">俄羅斯</a>進一步供應石油的制裁。此前美國在周四放寬了對印度煉油商購買俄羅斯原油的限制。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「財政部同意讓我們的盟友印度開始購買已經在海上的俄羅斯原油，」貝森特周五接受福克斯商業頻道採訪時說。「為緩解全球石油的臨時缺口，我們允許他們接收這些俄羅斯原油。我們可能會解除對其他俄羅斯原油的制裁。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:貝森特;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/貝森特\">貝森特</a>表示，目前海上有「數以億計的受制裁」原油。「從本質上講，通過解除制裁，財政部可以增加供應，」他說。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-1ff5c59d-3193-345d-a0cb-e512f6b53250-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Bessent Says US May ‘Unsanction’ More Russia Oil Post India Move</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
